[30;1m411 | [0m[35m# inside a loop that an augmented exception would have exited.[0m
[30;1m412 | [0m[35mif bool(os.environ.get("CRDS_TRAP_AUGMENTED", False)):[0m
[30;1m413 | [0m[35m    augment_exception = error_on_exception[0m
[30;1m414 | [0m[35melse:[0m
[30;1m415 | [0m[35m    augment_exception = exception_trap_logger(_reraise)[0m

[30;1m202 | [0m[35m    b64 = base64.b64encode(compressed)[0m
[30;1m203 | [0m[35m    ascii = b64.decode("ascii")[0m
[30;1m204 | [0m[35m    return dict(crds_encoded = "1.0",[0m
[30;1m205 | [0m[35m                crds_payload = ascii)[0m

[30;1m211 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m212 | [0m[35mcrds.bestrefs always computes best references with respect to a context which[0m
[30;1m213 | [0m[35mcan be explicitly specified with the `--new-context` parameter.  For JWST, if `--new-context`[0m
[30;1m214 | [0m[35mis not specified, the default build context is determined by checking the CRDS Server to find the[0m
[30;1m215 | [0m[35mappropriate context for the Calibration Software that a user has locally installed.[0m

[30;1m2 | [0m[35mUsing the CRDS Web Site[0m
[30;1m3 | [0m[35m=======================[0m
[30;1m4 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35mCRDS has websites at hst-crds.stsci.edu_, jwst-crds.stsci.edu_ and roman-crds.stsci.edu_ which suppo[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35mthe submission, use, and distribution of CRDS reference and mappings files.[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35mFunctions on the CRDS website are either *public* functions which do not require[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35mauthentication or *private* functions which require a CRDS login account.[0m

[30;1m2097 | [0m[35mclass UseAfterSelector(Selector):[0m
[30;1m2098 | [0m[35m    """A UseAfter selector chooses the greatest time which is less than[0m
[30;1m2099 | [0m[35m    the "date" condition and returns the corresponding item.[0m
[30;1m2100 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m2101 | [0m[35m[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m2177[0m[34m of [0m[33m2701[0m[31m ]--[0m

[30;1m1961 | [0m[35m            if weights[match_tuple] not in candidates:[0m
[30;1m1962 | [0m[35m                candidates[weights[match_tuple]] = [][0m
[30;1m1963 | [0m[35m            candidates[weights[match_tuple]].append(match_tuple)[0m
[30;1m1964 | [0m[35m        # Sort candidates into:  [ (weight, [match_tuples...]) ... ][0m
